data.text:
Photographer: Angel Marchini

Location:

Date:

"I have picked this particular photograph from my collection because it represents my love for classic soul artists such as Marvin Gaye, Curtis Mayfield and Barry White. I never had the chance to photograph them but I was there to photograph Gerald "Maxwell" Rivera aka the "Marvin Gaye of the '90s", the King of Neo-Soul."

Print Size: 20x24

Framed: Yes
